------------------------------------------------------------------------------
* Bug in tkmenu.tcl fixed.

------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Scidb 1.0 BETA (rev. #263)
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
* Experimental USE_TWO_BYTE_DECODING removed. A two byte decoding is slowing
down the position search time by factor 2.

------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Scidb 1.0 BETA (rev. #261)
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
* Experimental: (simple) two byte move decoding implemented (use compiler flag
USE_TWO_BYTE_DECODING).

* Fix in tkmenu.tcl.

